HEADWORD: Mestee
<hw>Mes*tee"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[See
<er>Mestizo</er>.]</ety> <def>The offspring of a white person and a
quadroon; -- so called in the West Indies.</def> <altsp>[Written also
<asp>mustee</asp>.]</altsp>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

